#

Savory Beef and Sweet Potato Hash with Fried Eggs

$12
450 kcal
Difficulty: 25%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Eggs

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinGluten Free

Tags:

HeartyComfort FoodEasy to Make

Description

A hearty and satisfying dish featuring seasoned beef, sweet potatoes, and perfectly fried eggs, all in one pan!

Ingredients

  • Ground beef: 1 pound
  • Sweet potatoes: 2 medium, diced
  • Onion: 1, chopped
  • Bell pepper: 1, chopped
  • Eggs: 4
  • Olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Garlic powder: 1 teaspoon
  • Smoked paprika: 1 teaspoon
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
